{"tid":1039503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【深圳好過香港，咁支那人麻煩唔好再落嚟香港獻世 R 著數】深圳GDP首越香港 成大灣區首位","createTime":"2019-02-27T12:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T13:52:00.000Z","uid":54337,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"48254cc6c54fd0c65fb3c8c8c8e4705dfd591e26","tid":1039503,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:30:45.000Z","msg":"【大灣區】深圳GDP首越香港 成大灣區首位<br />\n<br />\n香港統計處公布，去年香港的地區生産總值（GDP）為28453.17億港元，按年增3%，折合為24000.98億元（人民幣，下同）。而去年深圳市的GDP為24221.98億元，首次超越香港，居大灣區城市的首位。<br />\n<br />\n上述數據是據香港統計處網頁提供的港元與人民幣的兌換率計算，數據顯示，去年深圳的GDP高出香港221億元左右。目前，中國GDP頭五的城市依次為上海、北京、深圳、香港和廣州。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，廣州去年GDP的預計增速高達6.5%，遠高於香港的3%，而兩者GDP僅差約1000億元。因此，廣州生産總值可能在2019年超越香港。不過，香港去年的人均GDP為32萬元，廣州和深圳只有約15萬元。<br />\n<br />\n新興產業致深圳GDP急增<br />\n<br />\n據「東方財富網」分析，近年深圳的GDP快速增長，主要因其新興產業的穩步發展。根據官方數據，新興產業對深圳的GDP增長貢獻率達40.9%，而其生産總值從2012年的3878.22億元，增長至2017年的9183.55億元，漲幅達136.8%。<br />\n<br />\n針對深圳的GDP超越香港，「第一財經」引述深圳市委黨校副校長譚剛表示，這意味著深圳在大灣區中發揮的核心引擎作用將放大。他認為，深圳未來還要向其他城市學習，例如香港一流的營商環境和高等教育。"},{"pid":"bea4fa45b819b80cfe7d304e5fd65311642ad178","tid":1039503,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:30:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2281355/%E3%80%90%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E3%80%91%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3GDP%E9%A6%96%E8%B6%8A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%20%E6%88%90%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E9%A6%96%E4%BD%8D?mtc=30008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2281355%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%259C%25B3GDP%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25B6%258A%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%2520%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E9%25A6%2596%25E4%25BD%258D%3Fmtc%3D30008&d=7eOXcRQmrlFTo7mkgo38hGWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=66217cb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2281355/%E3%80%90%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E3%80%91%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3GDP%E9%A6%96%E8%B6%8A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%20%E6%88%90%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E9%A6%96%E4%BD%8D?mtc=30008</a>"},{"pid":"c3a64cc0a6dc17c2f2a5c0b5d8660a7b14f4c336","tid":1039503,"uid":44105,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:35:00.000Z","msg":"支那人得把口<br />\n死都唔會死番去"},{"pid":"3126f5bec0dfce661dd424df60b97766cf71b403","tid":1039503,"uid":17641,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>深圳萬歲!!</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b2764ccf8c83748d308bb6e1b52561b648b7e8","tid":1039503,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3a64cc0a6dc17c2f2a5c0b5d8660a7b14f4c336","tid":1039503,"uid":44105,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:35:00.000Z","msg":"支那人得把口<br />\n死都唔會死番去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:36:38.000Z","msg":"咬老綜，霸公屋，出雙糧，公園唱蝗歌袋貼士輕鬆袋每月2皮以上又唔使報稅"},{"pid":"7a8c4832b007e16ebb452e9856594e75ade25599","tid":1039503,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3126f5bec0dfce661dd424df60b97766cf71b403","tid":1039503,"uid":17641,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>深圳萬歲!!</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:36:58.000Z","msg":"深圳人民第一醫院萬歲"},{"pid":"068f8a22d419748143e75d51401acce5f5e587a4","tid":1039503,"uid":46801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:51:21.000Z","msg":"人均GDP呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1755be3f59d851a6eebd1f6784f5ad7285751cf","tid":1039503,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"068f8a22d419748143e75d51401acce5f5e587a4","tid":1039503,"uid":46801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T12:51:21.000Z","msg":"人均GDP呢<img src=\